{"article_id":"LsQE7U6BdLgFEyJS","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The Trump administration on Tuesday announced the \" orderly wind down \" of the Obama-era program","depth":9},{"id":1,"text":"that gave a deportation reprieve to illegal immigrants","depth":10},{"id":2,"text":"who came to the U.S. as children","depth":10},{"id":3,"text":"-","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"putting pressure on Congress to come up with a replacement .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"\" I do not favor punishing children ,","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"most of whom are now adults ,","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"for the actions of their parents .","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"But we must also recognize","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"that we are a nation of opportunity","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"because we are a nation of laws , \"","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"President Trump said , in a lengthy written statement","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"explaining the decision .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"The Department of Homeland Security formally rescinded the Deferred Action for Childhood Arrivals program ,","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"known as DACA ,","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"with a six-month delay for current recipients .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"According to Acting Homeland Security Secretary Elaine Duke ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"the interval is meant to give Congress \" time","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"to deliver on appropriate legislative solutions . \"","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"\" However , I want to be clear","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"that no new initial requests or associated applications","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"filed after today","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"will be acted on , \"","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"Duke said in a written statement .","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"The decision touched off a firestorm on Capitol Hill ,","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"where Democrats blasted the president","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"and Republicans blamed the prior administration","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"for putting Trump in a legal bind .","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"Attorney General Jeff Sessions ,","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"speaking to reporters ,","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"decried what he called the Obama administration 's `` disrespect for the legislative process ''","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"in enacting the 2012 policy .","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"He said","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"the \" unilateral executive amnesty \" probably would have been blocked by the courts anyway .","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"\" The executive branch , through DACA , deliberately sought to achieve what the legislative branch specifically refused to authorize on multiple occasions , \"","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"Sessions said ,","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"blaming the policy for the recent \" surge \" at the border .","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"\" Such an open-ended circumvention of immigration laws was an unconstitutional exercise of authority by the executive branch . \"","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"The Trump administration was facing a Tuesday deadline","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"to make a decision on DACA","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"or face legal action by Republican state AGs","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"who hoped to force the president ' s hand","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"in discontinuing the program .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"A day earlier , Sessions sent Duke a letter with his legal determination","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"that the 2012 executive action was unconstitutional .","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"Administration officials cast their approach Tuesday at the least disruptive option .","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"In his statement , Trump stressed","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"while new applications for work permits won ' t be accepted ,","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"\" all existing work permits will be honored until their date of expiration up to two full years from today . \"","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"Trump also said","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"applications in the pipeline will be processed .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"\" This is a gradual process , not a sudden phaseout , \"","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"he said .","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"\" Permits will not begin to expire for another six months ,","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"and will remain active for up to 24 months .","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"Thus , in effect , I am not going to just cut DACA off ,","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"but rather provide a window of opportunity","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"for Congress","depth":13},{"id":59,"text":"to finally act . \"","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"Trump vowed to resolve the issue \" with heart and compassion , \"","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"only this time working through Congress .","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"During the 2016 presidential campaign , Trump had promised to terminate DACA ,","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"though he appeared to soften his stance","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"since taking office .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"In ending the program with a six-month delay ,","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"Trump put the onus on Congress","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"to pass a legislative fix .","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"According to DHS ,","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"no current beneficiaries will be impacted before March 5 , 2018 .","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"\" Congress , get ready to do your job","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"- DACA ! \"","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"Trump tweeted Tuesday morning .","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"While some Republicans support the goals of the DACA program ,","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"many opposed the use of executive action","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"to institute it ,","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"describing the move as a presidential overreach .","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"Sen. Lindsey Graham , R-S.C. , is among those","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"who now support the call","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"to protect so-called \" Dreamers \" with legislation .","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"\" I have always believed","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"DACA was a presidential overreach , \"","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"he said in a statement .","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"`` However , I equally understand the plight of the Dream Act kids","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"who","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"-- for all practical purposes --","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"know no country other than America . \"","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"On a conference call , administration officials said Tuesday","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"they are still prioritizing criminal aliens for deportation .","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"But they described the original DACA criteria as very broad","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"and cited the legal determination of the Justice Department .","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"During the presidential campaign , Trump referred to DACA as \" illegal amnesty. \"","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"However , he seemed to edge away from that stance in April","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"when he told the Associated Press","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"that DACA recipients could \" rest easy . \"","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"The DACA program was formed through executive action by former President Barack Obama in 2012 ,","depth":6},{"id":96,"text":"allowing recipients to get a deportation reprieve","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"- and work permits -","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"for a two-year period","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"subject to renewal .","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"Under the program , individuals were able to request DACA status","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"if they were under the age of 31 on June 15 , 2012 ,","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"came to the U.S.","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"before turning 16","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"and have continuously lived in the country since June 15 , 2007 .","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"Individuals must also have a high school diploma , GED certification ,","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"been honorably discharged from the military","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"or still be in school .","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"Recipients can not have a criminal record .","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"Congress had been considering legislation","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"to shield young illegal immigrants from deportation","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"for years ,","depth":7},{"id":112,"text":"dating back to the George W. Bush administration .","depth":7},{"id":113,"text":"Lawmakers tried again to pass a bill during the Obama administration ,","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"but couldn ' t muster the votes","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"amid flagging Republican support","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"before Obama formed the program in 2012 .","depth":6},{"id":117,"text":"Nearly 800,000 undocumented youth are currently under the program 's umbrella .","depth":4},{"id":118,"text":"HILL REPUBLICANS REVIVE ' DREAM ACT ' TALKS","depth":3},{"id":119,"text":"AS TRUMP DECIDES FATE OF OBAMA PROGRAM","depth":3},{"id":120,"text":"On Friday , House Speaker Paul Ryan , R-Wis. , said","depth":6},{"id":121,"text":"he supported a legislative solution","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"to protect undocumented minors ,","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"but also urged the president to reconsider scrapping DACA .","depth":7},{"id":124,"text":"Following Tuesday 's announcement , however ,","depth":7},{"id":125,"text":"Ryan called DACA a \" clear abuse of executive authority \"","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"and urged Congress to act .","depth":8},{"id":127,"text":"\" Congress writes laws , not the president ,","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"and ending this program fulfills a promise","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"that President Trump made","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"to restore the proper role of the executive and legislative branches .","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"But now there is more to do ,","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"and the president has called on Congress to act , \"","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"he said in a statement .","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"\" At the heart of this issue are young people","depth":8},{"id":135,"text":"who came to this country through no fault of their own ,","depth":9},{"id":136,"text":"and for many of them it ' s the only country","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"they know . \"","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"Democratic National Committee Chairman Tom Perez said in a statement","depth":6},{"id":139,"text":"that , with the decision , `` Donald Trump has secured his legacy as a champion for cruelty . ''","depth":6},{"id":140,"text":"`` President Trump ' s decision","depth":8},{"id":141,"text":"to end DACA","depth":8},{"id":142,"text":"is a deeply shameful act of political cowardice and a despicable assault on innocent young people in communities across America , ''","depth":7},{"id":143,"text":"House Minority Leader Nancy Pelosi , D-Calif. , said in a statement","depth":6},{"id":144,"text":"Even as they blasted the president ,","depth":4},{"id":145,"text":"Democrats called for legislative action ,","depth":5},{"id":146,"text":"leaving open the possibility","depth":6},{"id":147,"text":"that the two parties could pass a bill in the coming months .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":295,"left":265,"right":294,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":265,"left":220,"right":264,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":220,"left":185,"right":219,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":185,"left":171,"right":184,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":171,"left":160,"right":170,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":160,"left":152,"right":159,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":151,"right":4,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":150,"right":3,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":0,"right":149,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent"